## Testing

- Use `bun test:run` for running tests (not `bun test` which uses watch mode)
- Watch mode can be resource-intensive and may cause issues in some environments
- Use `bun test:ui` for interactive debugging of failing tests
- Use `bun test:coverage` for coverage analysis before committing
